This paper focuses on measuring influence on Instagram, which is a social media platform. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SOC (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the paper discusses user statistics and regression models, which fall under the categories of cs.SI (Social and Information Retrieval) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also deals with visual content sharing, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper discusses the lack of relevant tools and metrics, which is related to human-computer interaction, falling under the category of cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
